// EXPECT_RUNTIME_PANIC panic from prelude
//
// Plan 62.B file-based runtime fns — `panic` actual runtime smoke
// (positive functional test, not just compile check).
//
// Verifies что `panic(msg)` declared в `std/prelude/runtime.nv` через
// `external fn panic(msg str) -> never`:
//   - Resolves через prelude facade auto-import (R27).
//   - Actually fires runtime panic (intercept в codegen → nv_panic).
//   - Возвращает never (compile-acceptable как single-expression body).
//
// До 62.B: panic был hardcoded в type-checker builtins HashSet +
// codegen special-case на name match. После 62.B: HashSet shrunk на
// 4 имени (panic/exit/assert/debug_assert), name-keyed intercept
// fires для AST Ident.

module plan62.panic_runtime_smoke

test "panic actually fires from prelude declaration" {
    panic("panic from prelude — Plan 62.B smoke")
}
